<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Min Profil</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg: #f8fafc;
            --card-bg: #ffffff;
            --accent: #2563eb;
            --text-main: #0f172a;
            --text-muted: #64748b;
            --border: #e2e8f0;
        }

        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--bg);
            margin: 0;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            color: var(--text-main);
        }

        .container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 450px;
            padding: 3rem 2.5rem;
            background-color: var(--card-bg);
            border-radius: 16px;
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
            text-align: center;
        }

        .avatar-placeholder {
            width: 64px;
            height: 64px;
            background: var(--bg);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 50%;
            margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
        }

        h2 {
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .status-text {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .links {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 10px;
        }

        .links a {
            display: block;
            padding: 0.75rem;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            transition: all 0.2s;
        }

        .btn-primary {
            background-color: var(--accent);
            color: white !important;
        }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            opacity: 0.9;
        }

        .btn-outline {
            background-color: transparent;
            color: var(--text-main);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
        }

        .btn-outline:hover {
            background-color: var(--bg);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="avatar-placeholder">👤</div>
        <h2>Din Profil</h2>
        <p class="status-text">Du er for øyeblikket ikke logget inn.</p>
        
        <div class="links">
            <a href="login" class="btn-primary">Logg inn</a>
            <a href="register" class="btn-outline">Opprett konto</a>
            <a href="/" class="btn-outline" style="margin-top: 10px; border: none; font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-muted);">Tilbake til forsiden</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>